      "span_text": "Assuming that the transparent oil droplets of birds, such as those of turtle, have in the red a refractive index 1.48, the refractive indices of the yellow and red oil droplets will be 1.48 þ 0.05 ¼ 1.53 and 1.48 þ 0.18 ¼ 1.66, so that the refractive index contrast with the cytoplasm for the T-, Y-and R-droplets becomes 0.14, 0.19 and 0.32."
